<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="instruction-n">instruction <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'strʌkʃn/    美 /ɪn'strʌkʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[正式用语] 教授；指导：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>receive <strong>instruction in</strong> computer
接受电脑培训</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They were given special instruction and practice in reading.
在阅读上他们得到了专门的指导和训练。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c-order">2.★ <strong>[C] [常用复数] 指示；命令 (order)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>receive <strong>instructions to do</strong> sth
接到命令做某事</p></div>

<h4 id="3-directions">3.★ <strong>[用复数] 用法说明；操作指南 (directions)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Read the <strong>instructions on</strong> medicine thoroughly.
仔细阅读药品说明。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Always read the <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (instruction) on the bottle carefully and take the right amount of medicine.  （2006 福建改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. instructions  </p></div>